    v2 = wp.exp(wp.sin((tmp + 0.46 * v0 + 0.46)))
    tmp = 0.11
    v2 = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.35) - wp.exp(v2 + 0.35)) + 0.46)
    v0 = tmp
    v0 = (0.81 + 0.83)
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.sin((v2 + 0.02 - v0 + 0.68)))
    data[tid] = v0
